    <h1>Ticket Rates and Subscriptions</h1>
    <p>
        RAT Craiova, representing the largest urban public transport operator in the Oltenia region, has as main objective, the
        organization of its activity so that the citizens can benefit from a quality, competitive service, based on safety and
        comfort.

        We also chose to offer our passengers some of the lowest travel rates nationwide, focusing on both the social nuance of
        the service provided and the issues resulting from the analysis of the purchasing power of citizens, in the context of
        the report price - quality.

        The tariffs currently practiced reside from the continuous study of the market, based on the demand and supply, of the
        costs and possibilities offered by RAT Craiova.

        By practicing these tariffs in favor of citizens, RAT Craiova does not neglect the aspects related to the quality of the
        environment, wanting to attract as many participants in public transport, to the detriment of using personal cars,
        influencing the reduction of pollutants and noise pollution and having a role active in decongesting traffic in our
        city.
    </p>
</div>

