<h2> Facilitate subscriptions </h2>
<article>
    <h3 class="ha">Retirees</h3>
    <p id="primul">
        According to HCL 144 / 28.04.2016, free subscriptions are granted for one year on all means of transport
        in Craiova to
        pensioners residing in Craiova, over 70 years of age or regardless of age and with an income of less than 1000 lei
        starting with 1 July 2016. HCL 37 / 26.01.2017 modifies the previous one and increases the revenues to 1100 lei
        starting
        with 01.02.2017 and 1200 lei starting with July 1, 2017.
    </p>
    <br>
    <h3 class="dis">People with Disabilities</h3>
    <p id="primul">
        According to order 290/609/2003, the Social Protection Department of Craiova City Hall grants free monthly
        subscriptions
        on all means of public transport in Craiova for people with severe and severe disabilities and their companions
        residing
        in Craiova.
    </p>

    <h3 class="dis">Pupils and Students</h3>
    <p id="primul">
        According to HCL 37 / 26.01.2017, a 50% discount is granted on the monthly subscription on all means of public transport
        in Craiova for pupils attending students authorized in the municipality of Craiova
    </p>

    <h3 class="dis">War Veterans and Descendants</h3>
    <p id="primul">
        According to law 44/1994, the monthly subscription is granted free of charge on all means of public transport in Craiova
        for war veterans domiciled in Craiova and 50% discount for their descendants
    </p>
</article>